<p>I decided to check out another one of those â€˜freeâ€™ tours and must say I highly recommend it here too. Thereâ€™s a lot of stuff you will easily miss, and a lot of stories you wonâ€™t hear about, if you donâ€™t go on one of these. Corruption, bureaucracy, severed hand in the church, statue of a girl that looks like a boy, and the ottomans building a number of very impressive baths all feature in the stories youâ€™ll hear.</p>

